on exitFrame
  [  0] pushint16 1 ............................. <1>
  [  3] pusharglist 1 ........................... <1>
  [  5] extcall 12 .............................. <soundBusy(1)>
  [  7] jmpifz [ 14] ............................ if soundBusy(1) then
  [ 10] pusharglistnoret 0 ...................... <>
  [ 12] extcall 13 .............................. nothing()
  [ 14] ret
end
